2. Multiply both sides by `‖P‖`:
   \[ \text{pc.fu\_outer P p.outerParams} \cdot \|P\| = ⟪rotM (p.θ₂) (p.φ₂) P, pc.w⟫. \]

3. But by definition of `p.outer`, we have:
